  section
    h2 Compatible with most CAM software
    .cam-logos
      img(src="images/cam/fusion360.png", alt="Fusion360 logo")
      img(src="images/cam/mastercam.png", alt="MasterCAM logo")
      img(src="images/cam/vcarve.png", alt="VCarve logo")
